{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"(1) Have you seen the one who denies the Recompense?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:2","price":"(2) For that is the one who drives away the orphan","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:3","price":"(3) And does not encourage the feeding of the poor.","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:4","price":"(4) So woe to those who pray","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:5","price":"(5) [But] who are heedless of their prayer[2000] -","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6202,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[2000]- i.e., the hypocrites who are unconcerned if they miss prayers when no one sees them.","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:6","price":"(6) Those who make show [of their deeds]","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6203,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"107:7","price":"(7) And withhold [simple] assistance.","arabic":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6204,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un","Chapter Al-Ma'un","Ma'un","Surah Ma'un","Chapter Ma'un","Al Ma'un","Surah Al Ma'un","Chapter Al Ma'un","Surah 107","Chapter 107","The Small Kindnesses","الماعون"]}